"procesamiento,\n"
"                    CPU, GPU y RAM de forma prácticamente ilimitada, con "
"ello es posible ejecutar simulaciones muy complejas como lo pueden ser "
"las que \n"
"                    utilizan el método de Montecarlo que requieren de "
"muchas iteraciones para disminuir su error. Además, el tener una "
"aplicación \n"
"                    en la web la hace accesible a prácticamente cualquier"
" persona en el mundo, investigadores y estudiantes de cualquier "
"universidad \n"
"                    pueden hacer uso de ella sin necesidad de instalar "
"algo en sus computadoras, solo es necesario tener acceso a internet."
msgstr ""
"With LightTrek, the aim is to leverage the capabilities offered by "
"various companies with <em>IaaS (Infraestructure as a service)</em>\n"
"                    or <em>Paas (Platform as a service)</em> offerings "
"such as Amazon with Amazon Web Services or Amazon Batch, which provide "
"virtually unlimited processing power, \n"
"                    CPU, GPU and RAM. This makes it possible to run "
"highly complex simulations, such as those \n"
"                    using the Monte Carlo method, which require numerous "
"iterations to reduce error. Furthermore, having a web application \n"
"                    makes it accessible to virtually anyone in the world."
" Researchers and students from any university \n"
"                    can use it without to install anything on their "
"computers; they only require internet access."

